                    </div>
                    <span>This is an intense and riveting story of talent, guts and luck. I would have left out some of the slightly gooey romanticism, but it's her story, not mine. <BR>She does a great job narrating on the audio cassette.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Excellent read</div>
